Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tougher drug laws
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xqt7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Sep 1986
Politicians seen to join the 'rush to righteousness' as the anti-drugs crusade takes on a vote-catching twist. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less